&lt;p&gt;Databases and data stores are at the center of our customers applications, the heart of our customers’ businesses. Datadog is embarking on a journey to revolutionize how databases are operated, flipping what is often seen as a black box of complexity prone to security and performance risks, into a well oiled machine that provides not just devops, developers and dbas with insights, but the business as well.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for an experienced product manager to lead a multifaceted product opportunity and team loaded with ambiguity and technical nuance, to accelerate this mission and this business within Datadog.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
